      "title": "CPC says four fuel shipments expected on July 17",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Four\u00a0fuel shipments are expected to arrive in Sri Lanka on the 17th of July, Ceylon Petroleum Corporation (CPC) says.",
        "According to the CPC, three diesel shipments of 40,000 metric tons each and 35,000 metric tons, as well as a shipment of Octane 92 Petrol are anticipated."
